name: Darrell Buchanan
text: Last time the pizza was excellent.

name: Theresa Maris
text: The Calzones are delicious.   We get them whenever we can.

name: Dee Helson
text: Always fresh food no matter what time i go in there

name: Rebecca Pittman
text: If you have time to wait it is great made to order food. Friendly staff and clean environment. Not to bad if you just want a quick bite to eat. Can always call ahead and order a pizza, wings or bread/cheese sticks this site also makes sub sandwiches to order (can also call that in).

name: brittany furlong
text: I love the minit mart the 2nd shift and 3rd shift people are great

name: John Robertson
text: Pizza is Usually really good. They have a good variety of different things to eat also

name: Jeffry Engert
text: It was good, but the pepperoni was salty
